This paper describes a Scheme implementation of miniAdapton, which is a system for incremental computation. Incremental computation is a topic that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the design and implementation of miniAdapton, which could be considered a topic in logic in computer science (cs.LO) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the portability of miniAdapton to other languages, which could be considered a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC).
